<span class=title>   waiting for a miracle</span><hr size=1> We wait, as Christians, for a miracle particularly during this time of Lent.<br>
<br>
And we wait, as a family, for a miracle for Jaci.  I don't know the shape of that event.  It might be in a healed body.  Or it might be in the promise of Christ.  But one way, or another, there is a miracle on the horizon.<br>
<br>
It's hard to wait.  Those last weeks of pregnancy are hard.  The last few days of school are seemingly endless.  And the last few miles before finally reaching Grandma's and Grandpa's house stretch out like eternity.<br>
<br>
But I believe there is value in the wait.  It prepares us for what is to come.  Even if we think we are ready.  Even if we think there is no preparation left to be done.  <br>
<br>
But waiting is still very hard.  Jaci, I am waiting for this coming miracle with you.  Every day, every minute, I wait with you.  When you feel that you are alone, there on the mountain and waiting, know that I am waiting with you in spirit as best I can.<br>
<br>
Love, Susan <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub98.ezboard.com/fbudignetfrm2.showPrevMessage?topicID=30.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub98.ezboard.com/fbudignetfrm2.showNextMessage?topicID=30.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fbudignetfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=30.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/prefabs/ez/addreply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fbudignetfrm2.emailToFriend?topicID=30.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fbudignetfrm2.threadControl?topicID=30.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/posticons/techops.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fbudignetfrm2.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=30.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fbudignetfrm2.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=30.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/unsubscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to stop receiving email notification of replies"> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies</a> <br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub98.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="budignetfrm1">Announcements<option value="budignetfrm2">General Di